### Create new user
POST http://localhost:3050/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name"        : "Dwi Prasetyo",
  "email"       : "dwi@example.com",
  "username"    : "dwi",
  "password"    : "1"
}

### Login to get token
POST http://localhost:3050/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email"       : "dwi@example.com",
  "password"    : "1"
}

